ontrolled, you could collide with either the bridge structure or the moored cruise ship, or run aground on the rocky banks. Your vessel carries one anchor with 90 metres of chain. The river bottom in this section is rocky gravel — anchor holding is uncertain. The nearest inland tug is based at Passau and can reach your position in approximately 25 minutes.',
